nodes.text: Kathleen Dee-Anne Stark (born April 26, 1956) is an American actress who portrayed Camie in Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope. Stark was originally considered for the role of Princess Leia, but instead landed the role of Camie, whose scene did not make it into the film's final cut.
Stark has also been a photographer and a model, and was once involved with Prince Andrew, Duke of York.
